function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	bEncounterActive = true
	--Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(ID_THIS_QUEST, S_POWER_SPAWN_ATTACK)
	idPing = Hydra.MinimapAddPing(ID_THIS_QUEST, 900, true)
	bPinged = true
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "ambushSpawner")
	
	local eliteSpawners = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elitePackSpawner")
	if #eliteSpawners > 0 then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elitePackSpawner")
		if worldTier == Hydra.WORLD_TIER_3 then
			nElitesSpawned = 2
			bElitePack = true
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elitePackSpawner")
		elseif worldTier == Hydra.WORLD_TIER_4 then
			nElitesSpawned = 3
			bElitePack = true
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elitePackSpawner")
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "elitePackSpawner")
		end
	end
	
--	for i = 1, #tNextSpawners do
--		Hydra.EventSendToActor("ADD_SPAWNER_PARENT", ID_THIS_QUEST, tNextSpawners[i])
--	end

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	nSpawnerRequestOn = nSpawnerRequestOn + 1

-- call the add parent event on linked spawners, then wait .5 seconds before checking parent/request again and spawning
-- (this is to cover an edge case where spawners could become active before all their parent spawners where cleared)
	if nSpawnerRequestOn == nSpawnerParents and bAddedSpawnParents == false then
		bAddedSpawnParents = true
		for i = 1, #tNextSpawners do
			Hydra.EventSendToActor("ADD_SPAWNER_PARENT", ID_THIS_QUEST, tNextSpawners[i])
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	if nSpawnerRequestOn == nSpawnerParents then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("Start_Stage", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	end
	
end

function Start()
	
	--send an event to add progress to the main quest
	local nProgress = 100 - nProgressSent
	if nProgress > 0 then
		Hydra.EventSend("FakeProgress", idSelf, nProgress)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	for i = 1, #tNextSpawners do
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("TURN_ON_SPAWNERS", ID_THIS_QUEST, tNextSpawners[i])
	end
	Hydra.MinimapRemovePing(idPing)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	local nProgress = math.floor(70/nEnemyCount)


	if Hydra.ActorIsInGroup(idActorKilled, "WE_Invasion_Normal") then
		nEnemyKilled = nEnemyKilled + 1
		Hydra.EventSend("FakeProgress", idSelf, nProgress)
		nProgressSent = nProgressSent + nProgress
	end
	
	if bReadyToEnd == true and bSpecialKilled == true and nEnemyKilled > nEnemyCount * fNextSpawnBreakpoint then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("EndEncounter", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if bElitePack then
		nElitesKilled = nElitesKilled + 1
		if nElitesKilled >= nElitesSpawned then
			bSpecialKilled = true
		end
		local nEliteVal = 30/nElitesSpawned
		Hydra.EventSend("FakeProgress", idSelf, nEliteVal)
		nProgressSent = nProgressSent + nEliteVal
	else
		bSpecialKilled = true
		Hydra.EventSend("FakeProgress", idSelf, 30)
		nProgressSent = nProgressSent + 30
	end
	
	if bReadyToEnd == true and bSpecialKilled == true and nEnemyKilled > nEnemyCount * fNextSpawnBreakpoint then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("EndEncounter", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	if Hydra.ActorIsInGroup(idActorSpawned, "WE_Invasion_Normal") then
		nEnemyCount = nEnemyCount + 1
	end
	
--	if bReadyToEnd == true and nEnemyKilled > nEnemyCount * fNextSpawnBreakpoint then
--		Hydra.EventSendToActor("EndEncounter", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
--	end

end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)

	bReadyToEnd = true
	Hydra.ActorFlagDynamicPrefabGroupForDespawn(idSelf, Hydra.DESPAWN_BEHAVIOR_LOCAL_EVENT)
	if bReadyToEnd == true and bSpecialKilled == true and nEnemyKilled > nEnemyCount * fNextSpawnBreakpoint then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("EndEncounter", ID_THIS_QUEST, ID_THIS_QUEST)
	end
	
end

function Start()
	if bPinged then
		Hydra.MinimapRemovePing(idPing)
	end
end
